    <title>gadget_searcher</title>
    <link href="https://blog.z2e4o6.com/2018/09/23/gadget-searcher/"/>
    <id>https://blog.z2e4o6.com/2018/09/23/gadget-searcher/</id>
    <published>2018-09-23T09:46:45.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-09-23T10:31:46.546Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pwn import *</span><br><span class="line">from capstone import *</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">class Gadget():</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">    def __init__(self, path):</span><br><span class="line">        self.elf = ELF(path)</span><br><span class="line">        self.text = self.elf.get_section_by_name(&apos;.text&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">        self.cmd = []</span><br><span class="line">        self.assm = []</span><br><span class="line">        self.addr = []</span><br><span class="line">        self.ve = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        self.ppr = []</span><br><span class="line">        if self.elf.bits == 32:</span><br><span class="line">            self.md = Cs(CS_ARCH_X86, CS_MODE_32)</span><br><span class="line">        else:</span><br><span class="line">            self.md = Cs(CS_ARCH_X86, CS_MODE_64)</span><br><span class="line">        self.gadget = []</span><br><span class="line">    def dissasm(self, data, adddr):</span><br><span class="line">        return  self.md.disasm(data, adddr)</span><br><span class="line">    def find_(self):</span><br><span class="line">        addr_ = self.text.header.sh_addr</span><br><span class="line">        tmp = self.dissasm(self.text.data(),addr_)</span><br><span class="line">        for i in tmp:</span><br><span class="line">            a = str(i.mnemonic+&quot; &quot;+i.op_str)</span><br><span class="line">            b = str(hex(i.address))</span><br><span class="line">            self.cmd.append(a)</span><br><span class="line">            self.addr.append(b)</span><br><span class="line">            print hex(i.address) + &quot; : &quot; + i.mnemonic +&quot; &quot; + i.op_str</span><br><span class="line">            self.ve[a] = b</span><br><span class="line">    def find_gadget(self,c):</span><br><span class="line">        self.find_()</span><br><span class="line">        buf = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        table = self.cmd</span><br><span class="line">        tmp = table.count(&apos;ret &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">        log.info(&quot;Analysing . . .  &quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        if tmp == 0:</span><br><span class="line">            log.info(&quot;No gadget(RET) found&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">            return -1</span><br><span class="line">        for i in range(0, tmp):</span><br><span class="line">            buf = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">            a = table.index(&apos;ret &apos;)</span><br><span class="line">            for j in range(a-c, a+1):</span><br><span class="line">                buf += table[j] + &quot;;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">            aa = self.ve[table[a-c]] + &quot; : &quot; + buf</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">            if table[a-c][:3] == &quot;pop&quot;:</span><br><span class="line">                self.ppr.append(self.ve[table[a-c]])</span><br><span class="line">            self.gadget.append(aa)</span><br><span class="line">            print aa</span><br><span class="line">            del table[a]</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">        return self.gadget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>경험삼아 대충 만들어봤던 gadget searcher다. 솔직히 정규 표현식 사용하면 더 간결한 코드로 작성할 수 있었겠지만 정확도… 는 핑계고. 그냥 귀찮았다. 별로 써본적도 없고.<br>~~ret 으로 끝나는 가젯밖에 찾지 못한다. 나중에 자동 솔버 작성할때 쓰려고 라이브러리 형식으로 구현해놨다.</p>]]></content>
    
